---
// Paths - First Steps / 90-day action paths
---

<section class="paths section" id="paths">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="reveal">
      <div class="section-label">First Principles Action</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">What do the first 90 days actually look like?</h2>
      <p class="section-body">The cost of building these systems is falling 10x per year. What required massive public investment five years ago can be prototyped today for a fraction. The binding constraint is no longer budget — it's political will. Here are the minimum necessary actions. <a href="/intelligent-economics/resources" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Download the data and methodology &rarr;</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="paths__grid">
      <div class="path-card path-card--featured reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="path-card__header">
          <div class="path-card__icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 34 L20 18" stroke="#00ff88" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/><path d="M20 24 C20 24 12 20 10 12 C16 12 21 17 20 24Z" fill="#00ff88" opacity="0.8"/><path d="M20 18 C20 18 28 16 30 8 C24 8 19 13 20 18Z" fill="#00ff88" opacity="0.5"/></svg></div>
          <span class="path-badge">Immediate</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="path-card__title">Prove the MIND Model</h3>
        <p class="path-card__desc">Before building anything physical, the mathematical foundation must be stress-tested and published. This is the Intelligence layer — collecting data, building measurement capacity. It gives policymakers something to point to and investors something to price.</p>
        <ol class="path-steps" role="list">
          <li class="path-step">
            <div class="path-step__num">1</div>
            <div class="path-step__text">Assemble a working group of economists to formalize the MIND Dashboard methodology — definitions, measurement protocols, baseline data sources</div>
          </li>
          <li class="path-step">
            <div class="path-step__num">2</div>
            <div class="path-step__text">Commission a retroactive MIND analysis of 3 existing economies to establish calibration baselines and validate the model against known outcomes</div>
          </li>
          <li class="path-step">
            <div class="path-step__num">3</div>
            <div class="path-step__text">Publish pre-print to SSRN and arXiv. Circulate to 50 target economists for peer review. Establish an open academic feedback loop</div>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div class="path-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="path-card__header">
          <div class="path-card__icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="15" y="16" width="10" height="18" rx="1" stroke="#00c8ff" stroke-width="1.8"/><rect x="5" y="22" width="8" height="12" rx="1" stroke="#00c8ff" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.7"/><rect x="27" y="20" width="8" height="14" rx="1" stroke="#00c8ff" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.7"/><line x1="3" y1="34" x2="37" y2="34" stroke="#00c8ff" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.4" stroke-linecap="round"/><rect x="18" y="24" width="4" height="5" rx="0.5" stroke="#00c8ff" stroke-width="1.2" opacity="0.5"/></svg></div>
          <span class="path-badge" style="background: var(--color-secondary-dim); color: var(--color-secondary);">60–90 Days</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="path-card__title">Identify Zone Zero</h3>
        <p class="path-card__desc">The first Symbiotic Zone needs a specific geographic and legal context. It doesn't need to be large — it needs to be real, monitored, and publicized.</p>
        <ol class="path-steps" role="list">
          <li class="path-step">
            <div class="path-step__num">1</div>
            <div class="path-step__text">Survey candidate jurisdictions: special economic zones, city-level partners, or sovereign-territory opportunities where experimental governance is legally possible</div>
          </li>
          <li class="path-step">
            <div class="path-step__num">2</div>
            <div class="path-step__text">Engage local policymakers with the published MIND framework. Seek a Memorandum of Understanding to pilot dual-currency accounting in parallel with existing systems</div>
          </li>
          <li class="path-step">
            <div class="path-step__num">3</div>
            <div class="path-step__text">Build the Zone's Guardian Lattice MVP: real-time MIND dashboard, Oracle Council selection protocol, and first AI Oracle deployment on public infrastructure data</div>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div class="path-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="path-card__header">
          <div class="path-card__icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="20" cy="20" r="12" stroke="#ffb400" stroke-width="1.8"/><path d="M20 12 L20 28 M15 16 Q20 14 25 16 M15 24 Q20 26 25 24" stroke="#ffb400" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round"/><circle cx="20" cy="20" r="6" stroke="#ffb400" stroke-width="1.2" opacity="0.4" stroke-dasharray="2 2"/></svg></div>
          <span class="path-badge" style="background: rgba(0,200,255,0.1); color: var(--color-tertiary);">Parallel Track</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="path-card__title">Design the Dual Currency</h3>
        <p class="path-card__desc">Foundation Coins and Culture Credits require technical infrastructure and legal architecture before they can be piloted. This work can begin immediately.</p>
        <ol class="path-steps" role="list">
          <li class="path-step">
            <div class="path-step__num">1</div>
            <div class="path-step__text">Form a monetary design team: cryptographers, monetary economists, and legal experts to specify the Foundation Coin minting protocol tied to computation for the intelligence commons</div>
          </li>
          <li class="path-step">
            <div class="path-step__num">2</div>
            <div class="path-step__text">Design Culture Credit demurrage mechanism: specify decay rate, circulation incentives, and the interface between Bit Economy and Atomic Economy exchange</div>
          </li>
          <li class="path-step">
            <div class="path-step__num">3</div>
            <div class="path-step__text">Prototype a closed-loop pilot within a single community: 500 participants, 6-month trial, full MIND reporting, and third-party audit of outcomes</div>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div class="path-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="path-card__header">
          <div class="path-card__icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M8 16 L8 24 L14 24 L24 32 L24 8 L14 16 Z" stroke="#ff6482" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linejoin="round"/><path d="M28 14 Q32 20 28 26" stroke="#ff6482" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round"/><path d="M31 11 Q37 20 31 29" stroke="#ff6482" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.5"/></svg></div>
          <span class="path-badge" style="background: rgba(255,180,0,0.1); color: #ffb400;">Always On</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="path-card__title">Make the Story Undeniable</h3>
        <p class="path-card__desc">The nucleation spreads through imitation. For that to work, the story of Zone Zero must be told so compellingly that the old world starts to look obviously obsolete.</p>
        <ol class="path-steps" role="list">
          <li class="path-step">
            <div class="path-step__num">1</div>
            <div class="path-step__text">Document everything in Zone Zero in real-time: MIND scores, human stories, before/after comparisons. Make the data radically transparent and beautiful</div>
          </li>
          <li class="path-step">
            <div class="path-step__num">2</div>
            <div class="path-step__text">Commission long-form journalism partnerships with major outlets to embed reporters in Zone Zero from day one — not press releases, but narrative journalism</div>
          </li>
          <li class="path-step">
            <div class="path-step__num">3</div>
            <div class="path-step__text">Build a public "MIND vs GDP" comparison dashboard that anyone can view — showing in real-time what the old metrics miss about what the new metrics reveal</div>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
